trans-unit.source: Obtains the file locations and descriptions of ASP.NET Web services.
trans-unit.target: Henter filplassering og beskrivelser av ASP.NET Web services.

trans-unit.source: The ContractSearchPattern class inherits from the abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoverySearchPattern> class and is employed by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler> class's <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> method, which handles an HTTP request for a discovery document.
trans-unit.target: ContractSearchPattern klassen arver fra abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoverySearchPattern>klasse og ansatt av den <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler>klassens <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A>metode, som behandler en HTTP-forespørsel for discovery-dokumentet.</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler.ProcessRequest%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryRequestHandler> </xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoverySearchPattern>

trans-unit.source: Normally, none of these classes need to be used directly by a developer.
trans-unit.target: Ingen av disse klassene må vanligvis brukes direkte fra en utvikler.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractSearchPattern"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractSearchPattern"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Creates the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference"></xref> object for the specified .asmx file.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference"> </xref> objektet for den angitte .asmx-filen.

trans-unit.source: The concrete <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference> class inherits from the abstract <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryReference> class.

A <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference> instance contains the location of the .asmx file and the corresponding Web Services Description Language (WSDL) document, which can be dynamically obtained by appending a wsdl query string to the .asmx file path.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference>forekomst inneholder plasseringen av .asmx-filen og det tilsvarende Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL)-dokumentet, som dynamisk kan oppnås ved å legge til en wsdl-spørringsstreng .asmx-filbane</xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference>

trans-unit.source: The file-system path of the Web service's .asmx file.
A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference"></xref> object with the specified file name for its .asmx file.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Discovery.ContractReference"> </xref> objektet med det angitte filnavnet for .asmx-filen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the file name pattern to use as a search target.
trans-unit.target: Henter filen navnet mønsteret som skal brukes som mål søk.

trans-unit.source: The pattern "*.asmx" indicates an ASP.NET Web service file extension.
trans-unit.target: Mønsteret "*.asmx" Angir filtypen for ASP.NET Web-tjenesten.
